      "rationale": "In-vitro tests conducted at 37°C, hematocrit 33±2%, per modified ASTM F1841. Testing covers 4 of 5 required operating points; the 3 L/min low-flow condition used a different anticoagulant protocol than the COU specification. Temperature control ±1°C within acceptable range. Traceability to ISO 10993-4 partial. Achieved level 3 against required 5."
