      "rationale": "NIH predictions compared against measurements at 5 operating points with relative errors ranging 5–9%. Formal validation metric (E_val) computed at 3 of 5 points with uncertainty bounds. Remaining 2 points use qualitative agreement assessment. No composite statistical comparison across all operating conditions. Achieved level 3."
