      "rationale": "Giersiepen-Wurzinger model selected based on prior literature use without systematic comparison to alternative hemolysis model forms. Model form uncertainty not quantified. At MRL 5 for a Class III device, this gap is critical. Factor not assessed to required level; achieved level 2 against required 5."
